<verse number="3" style="v" />Trust in Yahweh and do what is good;</para>

<para style="q1">settle in the land and graze in faithfulness.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Then delight yourself in Yahweh,</para>

<para style="q1">and he will give you the desires of your heart.</para>
